            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-semibold border-b border-gray-600">}\\mathbf{Pr}_{\\bm{G}\\in\\mathcal{G}_{n,k}}\\left\\{\\mathcal{D}(\\bm{G})=1\\right\\}-\\mathbf{Pr}_{\\bm{G}}\\left\\{\\mathcal{D}(\\bm{G})=1\\right\\}\\Big{</th>

