            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-semibold border-b border-gray-600">}\\texttt{Suc}_{\\mathsf{Rand}}(\\mathbb{A})-\\texttt{Suc}_{\\mathsf{McE}}(\\mathbb{A})\\Big{</th>

