    <h6 id="sec-17" class="text-base font-medium mt-4">Proof:</h6>

    <p class="text-gray-300">The number of elements in <span class="math">\\mathcal{B}_{r}</span> is given by the number of possible tuples <span class="math">(b,c,\\ell)</span> that is to say:</p>

