            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-semibold border-b border-gray-600">\\ 1\\leqslant s\\leqslant k,p_{s,k+i}\\neq 0\\right\\}\\setminus\\bigcup_{u=1}^{i-1}F_{i-u},$</th>

